    <entry>
      <title>编写 CNKI_2_BibTeX 过程的总结</title>
      <link href="/2019/01/16/CNKI-2-BibTeX/"/>
      <url>/2019/01/16/CNKI-2-BibTeX/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在两天多的爆肝之后终于完成了 <a href="https://github.com/Vopaaz/CNKI_2_BibTeX" target="_blank" rel="noopener">cnki2bib</a> 这个小工具，也打包发到了 <a href="https://pypi.org/project/cnki2bib/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PyPI</a> 上。写的第一个包，值得纪念下 233. 过程中也学到了很多东西，这里进行一下总结。</p><a id="more"></a><p>纪念一下两天的爆肝以及已经快 1600 次下载的优秀结果2333.</p><img src="https://s2.ax1x.com/2019/01/15/FzhSUK.png" width="400"><img src="https://s2.ax1x.com/2019/01/15/FzfzE6.png" width="300"><h2 id="文件引用路径">文件引用路径</h2><p>这是第一次写带着一些组织结构的项目，而不是以前那种只有一个文件或者全是同级文件夹下文件的托儿所项目了【升级到幼儿园x</p><p>整个项目的结构如下：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">📦CNKI_2_BibTeX</span><br><span class="line"> ┣ 📂cnki2bibtex</span><br><span class="line"> ┃ ┣ 📂misc</span><br><span class="line"> ┃ ┃ ┣ 📜__init__.py</span><br><span class="line"> ┃ ┃ ┣ 📜EntryInformationCheck.py</span><br><span class="line"> ┃ ┃ ┗ 📜EntryCore.py</span><br><span class="line"> ┃ ┣ 📜__init__.py</span><br><span class="line"> ┃ ┣ 📜cnki2bib.py</span><br><span class="line"> ┃ ┣ 📜cnkiNetEntries.py</span><br><span class="line"> ┃ ┗ 📜BibTexEntries.py</span><br><span class="line"> ┣ 📜.gitignore</span><br><span class="line"> ┣ 📜README.md</span><br><span class="line"> ┣ 📜setup.py</span><br><span class="line"> ┗ 📜requirements.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>过程中在进行各种 <code>import</code> 的时候就有些混乱，pylint 不停地都报错，显示“不存在这一模块”等等。这可能是因为 pylint 对 import 语句的检查是基于整个项目根目录 CNKI_2_BibTeX 的，而实际上有效的文件都在 cnki2bibtex 中，相互之间的引用实际上都以此作为根目录，这可能可以通过对 pylint 进行配置来解决，但是这次我没有研究。</p><p>总之在没有进行过特殊配置时就不要相信 pylint 的报错了，包括最后测试没有问题后，也一直有报错🙃，如何进行配置留待后续解决。</p><p>在不同文件运行时，VS Code 似乎是将运行的文件所在的目录作为根目录的，因此在 <code>EntryCore</code> 中引用 <code>EntryInformationCheck</code> 并在文件内调试正常的写法，在 <code>BibTexEntries</code> 中引用 <code>EntryCore</code> 并运行时会报错。具体的过程也很遗憾我没有记录下来【我懒得翻 git 的历史了【逃x】，这里只存档<strong>最终正常运行（以 <code>cnki2bib</code> 为入口）时</strong>的各个 <code>import</code> 语句，在开发下一个工具时提供参考。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># In cnki2bib.py</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> .BibTexEntries <span class="keyword">import</span> BibTeXContentStringFactory</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> .cnkiNetEntries <span class="keyword">import</span> CNKINetEntryFactory</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># In cnkiNetEntries.py and BibTexEntries.py</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> .misc.EntryCore <span class="keyword">import</span> Entry, NOT_FOUND_ANY</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> .misc.EntryInformationCheck <span class="keyword">import</span> checkBibEntryHasID, checkEntryHasValidFields</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># In EntryCore.py</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> .EntryInformationCheck <span class="keyword">import</span> RequiredFieldMissingException, checkEntryHasValidFields</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>总而言之根本的规则是，在同级文件前添加 “.”, 并以此向下引入。</p><p>注意在这样写完之后，在开发环境下通过命令行运行也会…报错 “No module named ‘__main__’”, 我也忘了当时是怎么调试的了orz, 但是打包分发后运行则一切正常。</p><p>可以考虑通过玄学来祈祷自己没有写错【x】</p><p>在过程中写外部的 test, 位置在 <code>cnki2bibtex\tests\test.py</code>, 此时若要引用则必须回到上级目录，当时的做法是这样的：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> sys</span><br><span class="line">sys.path.append(<span class="string">"."</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> .BibTexEntries <span class="keyword">import</span> BibTeXContentStringFactory <span class="comment"># Not sure whether this importation is right or not.</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>同样这里也懒得翻 git 历史记录了。总之这些问题都在于自己对于 Python import 路径的解析方式其实是一无所知，纯靠摸索。后续必须找时间看一下<a href="https://docs.python.org/3.7/reference/import.html?highlight=import" target="_blank" rel="noopener">文档</a>来搞清楚到底整个 import 路径该怎么写的问题。</p><h2 id="python-decorator-的使用">Python decorator 的使用</h2><p>最基础的装饰器写法非常容易，但是涉及到面向对象编程时，对于类或者类的实例的装饰器写法变得有些复杂。这此过程中有所涉及，在这里做一下记录。</p><h3 id="review-普通装饰器">Review: 普通装饰器</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">decorate</span><span class="params">(func)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">inner</span><span class="params">(*args,**kwargs)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">        doDecoratingBeforeThings()</span><br><span class="line">        res = func(*args,**kwargs)</span><br><span class="line">        doDecoratingAfterThings()</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> res</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> inner</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@decorate</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">funcToBeDecorated</span><span class="params">(*args,**kwargs)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    doSomeThing()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="类中函数的装饰器">类中函数的装饰器</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">decorate</span><span class="params">(func)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">inner</span><span class="params">(self,*args,**kwargs)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">        doDecoratingBeforeThings()</span><br><span class="line">        res = func(self,*args,**kwargs)</span><br><span class="line">        doDecoratingAfterThings()</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> res</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> inner</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Example</span><span class="params">(object)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">    @decorate</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">funcToBeDecorated</span><span class="params">(*args,**kwargs)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">        doSomeThing()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里的情况是装饰器函数定义在类之外，此时与普通装饰器之间的差别只在于多了一个 <code>self</code>, 没有其他任何更改。</p><p>对于装饰器函数定义在类内的情况此次没有涉及。</p><h2 id="项目打包以及分发">项目打包以及分发</h2><h3 id="dependency">Dependency</h3><p>在项目打包以及分发的环节，所涉及到的包包括：</p><ul><li>setuptools</li><li>twine</li><li>wheel</li></ul><p>其中【我记得】后两者是不在标准环境中的，尤其是在开发的 venv 环境下，需要 <code>pip install</code>.</p><h3 id="prepare-documents">Prepare documents</h3><p>在包的根目录下准备两个文件，<code>requirements.txt</code>, <code>setup.py</code>.</p><p>前者可以通过 <code>pip</code> 自动生成：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip freeze &gt; requirements.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里会录入所有当前的 venv 中安装的包，所以如果在开发过程中安装了其他的包后面又不需要，要记得删除。另外这里的版本号都是用等于号控制的，我想在绝大多数情况下应该修改成大于等于会更合适。</p><p>这个项目的 <code>setup.py</code> 如下：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> setuptools <span class="keyword">import</span> setup, find_packages</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">with</span> open(<span class="string">r'README.md'</span>,<span class="string">"r"</span>,encoding=<span class="string">"utf8"</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line">    long_description = f.read()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">setup(</span><br><span class="line">    name=<span class="string">'cnki2bib'</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    version=<span class="string">'0.1.0'</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    author=<span class="string">'Vopaaz'</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    author_email=<span class="string">"liyifan945@163.com"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    url=<span class="string">"https://github.com/Vopaaz/CNKI_2_BibTeX"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    description=<span class="string">'Converting the NoteExpress file (.net) exported by CNKI to BibTeX file (.bib)'</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    long_description = long_description,</span><br><span class="line">    long_description_content_type=<span class="string">'text/markdown'</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    packages=find_packages(),</span><br><span class="line">    include_package_data=<span class="keyword">True</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    install_requires=[</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">'Click'</span>,<span class="string">'jieba'</span>,<span class="string">'pyperclip'</span>,<span class="string">'pypinyin'</span></span><br><span class="line">    ],</span><br><span class="line">    entry_points=<span class="string">'''</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        [console_scripts]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        cnki2bib=cnki2bibtex.cnki2bib:launch</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    '''</span>,</span><br><span class="line">)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>里面的各个字段几乎都是自明的。需要尤其注意的是 <code>long_description_content_type='text/markdown'</code> 这个参数，如果不添加的话说明不会被按照 Markdown 的方式渲染。</p><p>另外， <code>entry_points</code> 参数是按照 <a href="https://click.palletsprojects.com/en/7.x/setuptools/#introduction" target="_blank" rel="noopener">click 的文档</a>写的，但在查找网络资料的时候发现广泛看见的写法和它有所不同。此次已经验证了用 <a href="https://click.palletsprojects.com/en/7.x/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">click</a> 来开发，这么写是没有问题的，如果以后不用这个工具【emm 大概率只会用它了？】，可能还要 double check 写法是否正确。</p><p><code>cnki2bib=cnki2bibtex.cnki2bib:launch</code> 本句中，第一个 <code>cnki2bib</code> 应该对应的是项目名称 <code>name='cnki2bib'</code>, 第二个 <code>cni2bibtex.cnki2bib</code> 对应的是 <code>cnki2bib.py</code> 这个文件，而 <code>launch</code> 是作为入口的函数名，而非固定字符串：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># In cnki2bib.py</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@click.command()</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@click.argument(some_args)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@click.option(some_args)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">launch</span><span class="params">(some_args)</span>:</span>  <span class="comment"># "launch" is the name of the function</span></span><br><span class="line">    operations()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="build-and-distribute">Build and Distribute</h3><p>完成了以上所有操作之后，运行以下命令：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python setup.py sdist bdist_wheel</span><br><span class="line">twine upload dist/*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>再根据提示输入 PyPI 账户的用户名和密码就可以完成上传和分发。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Coding </tag>
            
            <tag> Python </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>在 Hexo 中改变标签大小写</title>
      <link href="/2019/01/15/change-tag-case-in-Hexo/"/>
      <url>/2019/01/15/change-tag-case-in-Hexo/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>这两天发现以前使用的博客主题 <a href="https://github.com/frostfan/hexo-theme-polarbear" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> PolarBear</a> 模板不是很完善，有些功能是缺失的，而且那个界面实在是太…素雅了🤣。后来看文档发现 PolarBear 是基于 <a href="https://github.com/ahonn/hexo-theme-even" target="_blank" rel="noopener">even</a> 写的，因此今天干脆就决定替换到 even 这个主题。</p><a id="more"></a><p>顺手发现以前写的文章 tag, 首字母有的大写有的小写看得很不爽，所以就打算全部改成首字母大写统一格式。</p><p>结果就悲剧了…在网站的 <a href="/tags/">tags</a> 页面上能够正常显示大写，但是点进每一个具体的标签就会显示 404.</p><h2 id="解决方案">解决方案</h2><p>通过查看 Github 上的 Repository, 发现 tag 文件夹下的各个具体的 tag 各自有一个文件夹，标题是其名称，内有一个 index.html 页面。问题就出在这些文件夹的标题仍然是小写的，没有被同步为修改后的大写标题。查看本地的 .deploy_git 文件夹发现本地生成的 tag 文件夹下的小文件夹内容是正确的。</p><p>当时已经猜测到问题是 git 对于大小写是不敏感的，因此尝试了以下两个解决方法：</p><ul><li>删除整个 tags 文件夹，再重新 deploy</li><li>把所有已经改成大写的 tags 后面加 “1”, deploy, 再删除 “1”, deploy</li></ul><p>结果发现两个办法都无效，前者直接生成了小写文件夹名，后者在添加 “1” 后是大写，之后又变为小写。似乎是因为 git 已经保存了文件夹在小写名称时的快照，后续凡是有“忽略大小写”的重名，就会自然回到这个文件夹名称的版本。</p><p>后来开始查找资料，发现也已经有人遇到过同样的问题。</p><p>最终在<a href="https://stackoverflow.com/a/3011719/10838878" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这个回答</a>下发现，其实只要调整 git 的配置就可以将其设置成对大小写敏感…</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config core.ignorecase false</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>所以说到底其实是自己只用 git 客户端，而对工具本身没有了解，对命令一无所知的锅。后续要好好在这方面学习一下避免类似的情况发生。</p><hr><p><small>【下面部分和文章标题并没有什么关系【x </small></p><h2 id="miscellaneous">Miscellaneous</h2><p>在换主题的时候还顺便有一些其他有用的内容，一并记录在此。</p><h3 id="颜色">颜色</h3><p>首先是调整主题颜色的时候，挑选颜色挑了好久，最后选定了这三个：</p><figure class="highlight scss"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable">$theme-color</span>: <span class="number">#5096b9</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$deputy-color</span>: <span class="number">#ecececb0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$font-color</span>: <span class="number">#555555</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>分别：</p><blockquote><ul><li>作为 <a href=""> 超链接 </a> 以及像这样的引用模块的背景颜色</li></ul></blockquote><ul><li>代码块的背景颜色</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>所有主要字体的颜色</li></ul><h3 id="字体">字体</h3><p>在 <a href="/2019/01/11/CheatSheet-share/"><em>CheatSheet Share</em></a> 这篇文章中有提到过，<a href="https://github.com/georgd/EB-Garamond/blob/master/specimen/Specimen.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">EB Garamond </a> 这个字体真的惊为天人，但是考虑到很多电脑上并没有安装，可能起不到很好的效果。</p><p>这里在网站标题上采用 <font face="Garamond" size="5px">Garamond</font> 字体，尽可能近似，效果也还不错。</p><h3 id="列表渲染的问题">列表渲染的问题</h3><p>不知道是替换了主题还是在过程中不慎改变了 markdown renderer 的原因，多级列表无法正常显示，To-Do 列表也无法正常渲染。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">- Level 1</span><br><span class="line">  - Level 2</span><br><span class="line">    - Level 3</span><br><span class="line">- [ ] Todo 1</span><br><span class="line">- [ ] Todo 2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>以上代码会生成这样的效果：</p><ul><li>Level 1<ul><li>Level 2<ul><li>Level 3</li></ul></li></ul></li><li>[ ] Todo 1</li><li>[ ] Todo 2</li></ul><p>但是这应该是多层列表的标准语法，目标效果：</p><img src="https://s2.ax1x.com/2019/01/15/Fzbq2V.png" width="200"><p>暂时只能通过避免使用这两个功能，留待以后解决。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Hexo </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>代码整洁之道 Notes-1</title>
      <link href="/2019/01/12/cleanCode-Note1/"/>
      <url>/2019/01/12/cleanCode-Note1/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>寒假阅读的第一本书是《代码整洁之道》，回想起自己以前写代码的时候犯下的一些错误，给自己后面带来的麻烦，书中都有提到，读来确实感觉有很多收获。</p><p>在笔记中也主要是记录自己没有注意的内容，将一些可能很重要但是平时已经做到的内容省略。</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="命名">命名</h2><ul><li>避免误导：编程语言中可能有很多专有类型，例如 <code>List</code>, 如果某个变量不是这种类型，就不要将这个关键字用于命名，例如 accountList, 可以用 accountGroup 等代替</li><li>尽量用长名字描述清楚变量的含义，不要使用简短的名字或是缩写</li><li>将各种常量都定义为可以搜索的名称，这将便于搜索和后续的修改</li></ul><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// Wrong:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(classroom.studentNumber &gt; <span class="number">40</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    doSomeThing();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// Correct:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">final</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> MAX_STUDENTS_PER_CLASS = <span class="number">40</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(classroom.studentNumber &gt; MAX_STUDENTS_PER_CLASS)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    doSomeThing();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>将一整个工程/模块中的同一个概念对应同一个词，例如以下三者不要混用<ol><li>controller</li><li>driver</li><li>manager</li></ol></li></ul><h2 id="函数">函数</h2><blockquote><p>函数的第一规则是要短小，第二条规则是还要更短小。函数应该只做一件事。</p></blockquote><ul><li>尽最大可能地拆分函数。</li><li><code>if-else</code> 语句和 <code>while</code> 语句中的代码块应当尽量短小，可以拆分另一个函数出来用于专门处理这种情况，尽量避免多重嵌套</li><li>对“函数应该只做一件事”的详细解释：做的事情在同一抽象层面上</li></ul><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// High level</span><br><span class="line">obj.getHtml()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">// Low level</span><br><span class="line">obj.append(<span class="string">"\n"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><span id="to"></span></p><ul><li>函数的整体组织形式应当可以用 “To” 语言来清晰地，自顶向下地描述：<ol><li><strong>To</strong> do A, firstly do B, if C, then do D</li><li><strong>To</strong> do B, firstly do B1, then do B2</li><li><strong>To</strong> judge C, firstly do E, then judge F</li><li><strong>To</strong> do D, firstly do D1, then do D2</li></ol></li><li>注意每一行 To 仅仅只能对应 1 个函数，并且这行描述应当是简洁而清晰的。如果过长则说明应当拆分函数。</li></ul><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">A</span><span class="params">(*args, **kwargs)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    B()</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> C():</span><br><span class="line">        D()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">B</span><span class="params">(*args, **kwargs)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    B1()</span><br><span class="line">    B2()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">C</span><span class="params">(*args, **kwargs)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    E()</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> F()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">D</span><span class="params">(*args, **kwargs)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    D1()</span><br><span class="line">    D2()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="函数参数">函数参数</h3><ul><li>函数参数地数量应当越少越好，如果超过了 3 个，则必须进行封装，将逻辑上有关联的几个变量封装成一个 <code>class</code></li><li>不要使用“输出参数”，即函数返回值为 <code>void</code>, 而对于其中某一个参数进行转换。这不直观，也不符合正常人的思维方式</li><li>当一个函数要对某些实体的状态作出修改时，只能够修改其所属的对象的状态</li></ul><p>刚开始学 Python 的时候对于 <code>list</code> 的两个排序分不清楚，看到这里就豁然开朗，而且觉得这是个很好的例子了：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sorted(theList)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># The List itself is not changed, the function returns a new list which is sorted.</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">theList.sort()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Return None, as it is a "behavior", having no meaning for return value intuitively.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Instead, it change the arrangement of the object that "sort()" belongs to: "theList".</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>绝对不使用标识函数（某个输入变量为 <code>boolean</code>, <code>True</code> 代表做某件事，而 <code>False</code> 代表做另一件事）。这直接违反了一个函数只做一件事的原则，应当将其拆分为 <code>doSomeThingForCaseA()</code>, <code>doSomeThingForCaseB()</code> 两个函数</li><li>如果一个函数有两个参数，那么两者的位置就可能在使用时搞反。虽然现在的 editor 或者 IDE 可能有提示的功能，但是有时候提示确实没有那么好用。</li></ul><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">boolean</span> <span class="title">assertEquals</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> expected, <span class="keyword">int</span> actual)</span></span>; <span class="comment">// Easy to place the params in the wrong order.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">boolean</span> <span class="title">assertExpectedEqualsActural</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> expected, <span class="keyword">int</span> actual)</span></span>; <span class="comment">// A better choice</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在之前为了 java 考试写轮子的时候，就遇到过这个错误，当时在考场上还造成了一些小问题。</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">write_txt</span><span class="params">(String path, String text)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// Misplace path with text on the exam.</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">writeTextIntoFilePath</span><span class="params">(String text, String filePath)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// If it was changed into this, things will be much better.</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>保证函数没有<strong>副作用</strong>，不做它没有声明要做的任何事情:</li></ul><p>例如在 <code>checkValidPassword()</code> 中，不能够因为 password 被验证是 valid, 就进行 login, open new session 等操作。这一问题在我写下载网络学堂文件的脚本中也出现，但是这里无法上 code 示例因为写的真的太差已经删了【】</p><ul><li>函数要么做什么事，要么回答什么事，两者不可兼得。如果函数做什么事情之后可能出错，直接 raise Exception, 而不是通过返回错误码</li><li>try-catch 代码块中应当只有一行代码，调用一个函数来专门处理错误的情况，这样可以保证主函数逻辑清晰。因为处理异常本身已经是一件足够复杂的事情。</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Coding </tag>
            
            <tag> Notes </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
